<p><b>law on domestic violence (Brazil); 
</b></p>
<p>117.62. <b>Take further legislative and practical measures to end violence 
</b></p>
<p><b>against women, including the phenomenon of bride kidnapping as well as early 
</b></p>
<p><b>and forced marriage (Austria); 
</b></p>
<p>117.63. <b>Strengthen the implementation of legislation aimed at the elimination 
</b></p>
