<p><b>abuses and uphold individual freedoms in the country (Norway); 
</b></p>
<p>117.106. <b>Ensure that its legislation protects the rights of everyone, regardless 
</b></p>
<p><b>of their sexual orientation and gender identity, minority status or any other 
</b></p>
<p><b>basis, to freedom of expression and assembly, freedom from discrimination and 
</b></p>
