</b></p>
<p>117.107. <b>Ensure respect for freedom of expression, freedom of the press and 
</b></p>
<p><b>freedom of association (France); 
</b></p>
<p>117.108. <b>Guarantee freedom of assembly and association in line with ICCPR 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Germany); 
</b></p>
<p>117.109. <b>Ensure in law and practice that journalists and other persons can 
</b></p>
